text: Charlene Woitha (born 21 August 1993) is a German athlete who specialises in the hammer throw. She qualified for 2016 Summer Olympics. She finished in 29th place in the qualifying round and did not advance to the final. == Personal bests == {| class="wikitable" |- ! Event !! Record !! Venue !!
